# Diagnostic bundles are produced by `python3 build.py`. The 5+ GiB
# encrypted logd artifacts and the matching JSON metadata should be
# generated per-build and uploaded via the PR description, not
# committed to the repo. Existing diagnostic/ entries in git history
# predate this rule and stay in the tree until they are removed.
diagnostic/
tmp/

